overview.en: The goal is to use the block chain technology to improve the traceability of international logistics and imported goods. Through the de-centralized design, the entire commodity sales circle will be purified. Meanwhile, players holding tokens will enjoy more concessions and global logistics transactions will be more convenient.
overview.zh: NTERNATIONAL ITEM CHAIN目标利用区块链技术改善国际物流及进口货物溯源情况，通过去中心化的设计，让整个商品销售圈净化化境，同时让持有代币的玩家享受更多优惠，让全球物流交易更加便利。
